text: Xihuayuan Subdistrict () is a subdistrict in Xixia District, Yinchuan, Ningxia, China. , it has 13 residential communities under its administration. == See also == * List of township-level divisions of Ningxia == References == Category:Township-level divisions of Ningxia Category:Yinchuan
